snippet.title: Catherine O'Hara Tribute
snippet.description:
From Moira Rose to Delia Deetz, she's given us characters we can't forget! Join us as we celebrate the incredible career of Catherine O'Hara. Our tribute includes her iconic roles in "Beetlejuice," "Home Alone," "Schitt's Creek," and so much more! Which of her performances has made you laugh the hardest? Let us know in the comments below! We'll explore her early days with SCTV, her collaborations with Christopher Guest, her unforgettable voice acting in "The Nightmare Before Christmas," and how she's brought her unique comedy style to everything from blockbuster films to award-winning television.
